Invocation Name: cloud fact
des:
You can start learning AWS by saying: Alexa, start cloud fact.

"Tell me an S3 fact", "I want to learn about DynamoDB", "tell me something about EC2".

Currently, only S3, DynamoDB, and EC2 are supported.
